WEBVTT

01:40.380 --> 01:48.740
[You are My Fateful Love]
[EP04]

01:53.860 --> 01:54.860
Mr. Xu?

01:58.459 --> 01:59.339
Why're you back?

02:00.459 --> 02:01.539
Didn't you say we'd meet at the firm?

02:07.419 --> 02:08.259
What's this?

02:10.020 --> 02:11.419
Cen Sisi's backup plan.

02:36.660 --> 02:37.819
Such a fake angel!

02:41.299 --> 02:42.019
Sorry,

02:42.019 --> 02:42.699
got carried away.

02:44.139 --> 02:44.979
"Fake angel" means?

02:47.699 --> 02:49.579
Check the mirror.

02:53.579 --> 02:54.780
Got a question though.

02:55.139 --> 02:56.180
How'd you reach

02:56.180 --> 02:57.060
The Poet?

02:57.380 --> 02:58.620
I tried before,

02:58.620 --> 03:00.100
but she was always shady.

03:00.579 --> 03:01.500
She only agreed

03:01.500 --> 03:02.500
to a statement.

03:03.259 --> 03:04.220
Now she's

03:04.539 --> 03:05.979
playing undercover…

03:07.019 --> 03:08.340
We're pros,

03:08.780 --> 03:10.819
got our own tricks.

03:11.220 --> 03:12.500
Otherwise why

03:12.500 --> 03:13.660
would you pay us?

03:16.620 --> 03:17.859
So with someone like Cen Sisi,

03:17.859 --> 03:19.100
stirring trouble on purpose

03:19.180 --> 03:19.900
and being

03:19.900 --> 03:20.859
two-faced,

03:21.699 --> 03:22.979
my dear pros,

03:23.220 --> 03:24.019
what's our

03:24.019 --> 03:25.019
next move?

03:35.180 --> 03:36.019
[If she asks later]

03:36.019 --> 03:37.060
[what the next move is,]

03:37.380 --> 03:40.500
[just say block the defendant.]

03:42.699 --> 03:43.500
[Why?]

03:44.139 --> 03:44.900
[Be a real lawyer,]

03:44.900 --> 03:45.900
[ok?]

03:46.380 --> 03:47.699
[Time to lock down]

03:47.699 --> 03:49.019
[online evidence again.]

03:49.979 --> 03:50.620
[I know.]

03:51.060 --> 03:52.579
[Just say what I told you.]

03:56.139 --> 03:57.180
If you really

03:57.180 --> 03:58.419
hate her that much,

03:58.699 --> 03:59.940
just block her.

04:00.139 --> 04:01.060
What are you, a kid?

04:05.620 --> 04:06.460
Now the evidence

04:06.460 --> 04:07.259
is right here,

04:07.380 --> 04:08.780
of course we'll help the client

04:08.780 --> 04:10.739
lock down online evidence again.

04:11.660 --> 04:13.380
[Those two guys…]

04:16.139 --> 04:17.299
Yeah…

04:18.380 --> 04:19.139
Right.

04:22.460 --> 04:23.780
Mr. Liu,

04:24.700 --> 04:25.780
shouldn't say this but,

04:26.619 --> 04:28.619
as a partner here,

04:28.939 --> 04:30.100
you really need to level up

04:30.100 --> 04:31.100
your case handling

04:31.100 --> 04:32.179
and your skills.

04:33.179 --> 04:33.660
From your

04:33.660 --> 04:34.460
performance on

04:34.460 --> 04:35.419
this case,

04:36.660 --> 04:37.260
I suggest

04:37.340 --> 04:39.739
I take the lead.

04:42.059 --> 04:44.140
[They're already at each other's throats?]

04:47.220 --> 04:48.100
Well.

04:49.619 --> 04:50.539
Very well!

04:51.260 --> 04:52.619
Sure!

05:01.020 --> 05:03.260
[Mr. Liu, don't take it to heart.]

05:03.900 --> 05:05.140
[Huaisong,]

05:05.140 --> 05:06.499
[you sly fox!]

05:13.379 --> 05:14.539
Thanks, both of you.

05:15.419 --> 05:16.419
Got her number?

05:17.179 --> 05:18.020
You mean Cen Sisi?

05:18.419 --> 05:18.859
Yeah.

05:19.179 --> 05:19.580
I have.

05:21.379 --> 05:23.059
Know how to record calls?

05:24.739 --> 05:26.299
You mean she doesn't know

05:26.299 --> 05:27.499
The Poet sold her out,

05:28.059 --> 05:29.100
and I can play dumb

05:29.100 --> 05:29.780
to get her talking?

05:34.059 --> 05:34.859
I have no idea.

05:35.780 --> 05:37.100
Can you teach me?

05:40.499 --> 05:41.419
How to record

05:41.419 --> 05:42.419
a call properly?

05:43.499 --> 05:45.020
We should try to guide them

05:45.020 --> 05:46.820
to confirm identity first.

06:11.859 --> 06:12.739
Cut to the chase.

06:15.419 --> 06:16.220
Got it.

06:16.499 --> 06:17.460
No dragging it out

06:17.460 --> 06:18.499
with her,

06:18.660 --> 06:20.299
get her to spill fast.

06:20.979 --> 06:21.499
Exactly.

06:22.260 --> 06:23.179
Got confidence?

06:24.900 --> 06:26.419
I know her mindset,

06:26.900 --> 06:27.660
worth a shot.

06:28.979 --> 06:30.220
Tomorrow at noon,

06:30.220 --> 06:30.979
I'll call her.

06:31.340 --> 06:32.900
That time's just after lunch,

06:33.260 --> 06:34.059
brain's low on blood,

06:34.379 --> 06:35.580
she won't react fast.

06:35.939 --> 06:37.260
Might not get suspicious.

06:45.419 --> 06:46.020
Yu,

06:46.340 --> 06:47.820
so tomorrow after lunch,

06:48.220 --> 06:49.419
won't your focus

06:49.780 --> 06:51.220
dip too?

06:52.499 --> 06:53.379
Don't worry, Mr. Liu,

06:53.780 --> 06:54.820
I'll eat early.

06:55.700 --> 06:56.140
Fine.

06:57.660 --> 06:58.580
Speaking of food,

06:58.900 --> 06:59.739
should we

06:59.739 --> 07:00.859
grab dinner now?

07:04.140 --> 07:04.939
It's late.

07:05.619 --> 07:06.379
Sorry

07:06.379 --> 07:07.179
for keeping you.

07:08.179 --> 07:08.939
How about I treat you…

07:12.020 --> 07:13.020
and Mr. Xu

07:13.299 --> 07:14.220
to dinner?

07:14.619 --> 07:15.179
Sure.

07:25.100 --> 07:26.140
Director,

07:26.379 --> 07:27.820
just give my phone back.

07:27.820 --> 07:28.739
I promise I won't

07:28.739 --> 07:29.780
play again.

07:29.780 --> 07:31.299
Really, never again!

07:31.739 --> 07:34.260
Director, don't give it back.

07:34.260 --> 07:35.900
She'll play again.

07:35.900 --> 07:37.020
She really will!

07:38.179 --> 07:38.900
What are you two doing?

07:39.220 --> 07:40.499
Doing a comedy skit?

07:40.979 --> 07:41.979
Call home already!

07:42.220 --> 07:42.859
Director,

07:42.859 --> 07:44.460
my parents are abroad.

07:45.059 --> 07:45.859
So?

07:46.179 --> 07:47.419
Abroad, they've got no phone?

07:47.739 --> 07:48.379
No signal?

07:48.939 --> 07:49.900
Listen up,

07:50.220 --> 07:52.220
no call today,

07:52.220 --> 07:53.299
no one leaves.

07:54.100 --> 07:55.299
Think I can't even handle you two?

08:03.700 --> 08:04.419
Big shot, huh?

08:14.739 --> 08:15.460
Abroad, right?

08:21.499 --> 08:22.020
Hello,

08:23.260 --> 08:24.059
I'm Feng Zhu,

08:24.379 --> 08:25.460
Huaishi Xu's teacher.

08:25.900 --> 08:26.460
Today…

08:26.939 --> 08:27.340
This…

08:27.939 --> 08:28.939
You can speak Chinese?

08:29.379 --> 08:30.140
Great.

08:30.460 --> 08:31.020
Here's the thing.

08:31.020 --> 08:32.739
I'm Zhu Feng, head of moral ed

08:32.939 --> 08:33.379
at First High-School.

08:34.580 --> 08:35.220
Today,

08:35.220 --> 08:36.619
Huaishi broke school rules

08:36.739 --> 08:38.419
and brought her phone.

08:38.739 --> 08:39.859
First time

08:39.859 --> 08:40.820
I noticed,

08:40.820 --> 08:42.420
but the issue's…

08:42.859 --> 08:43.619
[Sorry,]

08:43.779 --> 08:44.700
I can't handle it

08:44.700 --> 08:45.619
at the moment.

08:46.300 --> 08:47.139
Please contact

08:47.139 --> 08:47.899
her guardian.

08:48.340 --> 08:49.739
Number 133…

08:50.100 --> 08:50.859
Hold on.

08:52.979 --> 08:53.540
Bro,

08:53.899 --> 08:55.540
[that's betrayal]

08:55.540 --> 08:56.379
[and revenge!]

08:57.340 --> 08:58.540
You're getting back at me

08:58.739 --> 08:59.779
for peeking at your texts.

09:01.019 --> 09:01.540
By the way,

09:01.899 --> 09:02.820
this isn't the first time

09:02.820 --> 09:04.019
she brought her phone.

09:04.700 --> 09:05.180
Once you

09:05.180 --> 09:06.540
reach her guardian,

09:07.220 --> 09:08.420
please explain

09:08.420 --> 09:10.100
her lying clearly.

09:10.580 --> 09:11.499
Got it,

09:12.139 --> 09:12.540
thanks

09:12.540 --> 09:13.580
for your help.

09:13.979 --> 09:14.659
That's it.

09:14.659 --> 09:16.180
Won't bother you more, bye.

09:22.899 --> 09:23.820
1,000-word check.

09:24.300 --> 09:25.499
Put it on my desk

09:25.659 --> 09:26.540
before class tomorrow.

09:28.779 --> 09:29.540
What?

09:30.659 --> 09:31.340
Why laughing?

09:33.019 --> 09:33.779
1,500 words for you!

09:37.979 --> 09:39.460
You and your sister

09:39.460 --> 09:40.540
don't get along, do you?

09:41.420 --> 09:42.700
She's in trouble,

09:42.700 --> 09:43.859
and you didn't even cover for her.

09:44.499 --> 09:45.700
She has caused

09:48.139 --> 09:49.180
enough trouble.

09:49.899 --> 09:50.700
Can't fix it all.

09:57.100 --> 09:58.700
Thanks so much,

09:58.700 --> 10:00.060
Lawyers Xu and Liu

10:00.139 --> 10:00.940
for looking out for me.

10:01.619 --> 10:02.139
Yu,

10:02.460 --> 10:03.739
you're too polite.

10:03.859 --> 10:04.779
This is our job.

10:06.619 --> 10:08.180
I'm driving, so no drinks.

10:09.700 --> 10:10.859
Then have something else.

10:11.899 --> 10:12.700
A cola for you?

10:14.940 --> 10:15.580
Unhealthy.

10:19.540 --> 10:19.979
Hello,

10:20.300 --> 10:21.340
a lemonade,

10:21.420 --> 10:21.859
please.

10:22.180 --> 10:22.700
Sure.

10:23.739 --> 10:24.540
Yu, cheers.

10:27.899 --> 10:29.540
Yeah, work stress,

10:29.859 --> 10:30.979
better to drink something healthy.

10:31.460 --> 10:31.940
Yeah.

10:49.460 --> 10:50.820
Here, try this.

10:58.580 --> 10:59.340
Know them?

11:12.820 --> 11:14.100
Miss Ruan, a reminder.

11:14.460 --> 11:15.379
Taking photos

11:15.379 --> 11:16.859
without permission

11:17.100 --> 11:18.340
has legal risks.

11:21.300 --> 11:22.139
I'm not just snapping photos,

11:22.139 --> 11:23.180
I'm throwing punches too.

11:24.060 --> 11:24.700
Need help?

11:24.820 --> 11:25.580
No, private matter.

11:27.019 --> 11:28.139
That perfume

11:28.659 --> 11:29.580
smells great.

11:29.899 --> 11:31.659
Picked it just for you.

11:32.340 --> 11:33.420
Fits your elegance,

11:33.420 --> 11:34.420
right?

11:34.700 --> 11:35.340
Really?

11:35.820 --> 11:36.820
I bought it with

11:36.820 --> 11:37.739
your girlfriend.

11:38.019 --> 11:39.100
Why don't I think

11:39.100 --> 11:39.420
it fits

11:39.420 --> 11:40.580
her vibe?

11:42.100 --> 11:44.019
Yu, fancy meeting you here.

11:44.499 --> 11:46.580
Yeah, what a coincidence.

11:47.019 --> 11:48.060
If not,

11:48.420 --> 11:49.619
I wouldn't see this.

11:52.100 --> 11:53.379
Who do you think that guy is?

11:54.700 --> 11:55.820
Didn't you hear her?

11:56.180 --> 11:56.859
Private matter.

11:58.540 --> 11:59.739
Definitely an ex.

12:01.540 --> 12:02.659
Just an ex,

12:03.100 --> 12:04.139
worth getting this mad?

12:05.580 --> 12:07.940
No love, no hate.

12:09.100 --> 12:10.940
Still not over it.

12:17.060 --> 12:17.940
Let me introduce.

12:18.619 --> 12:19.340
This is Ms. Lin,

12:19.340 --> 12:20.700
my business partner.

12:22.139 --> 12:22.899
And this is my…

12:22.899 --> 12:24.619
I'm Zhang Chuan's girlfriend's bestie.

12:27.420 --> 12:28.499
Ms. Lin, you probably didn't know

12:28.779 --> 12:29.779
he has a girlfriend, right?

12:31.019 --> 12:31.779
Well,

12:32.460 --> 12:33.300
business is business,

12:33.300 --> 12:34.259
not romance.

12:34.659 --> 12:35.940
No need to share personal stuff.

12:36.739 --> 12:37.700
Right, Chuan?

12:38.899 --> 12:39.460
Right.

12:45.540 --> 12:47.300
Many want to do business with me,

12:47.859 --> 12:48.899
who are you?

12:49.619 --> 12:51.139
Why should I deal with you?

12:53.940 --> 12:54.420
Ms. Lin…

13:01.100 --> 13:02.659
Yu, you misunderstood me.

13:02.659 --> 13:03.460
Misunderstood what?

13:03.460 --> 13:04.379
I really…

13:05.340 --> 13:06.100
What's going on?

13:10.139 --> 13:10.779
Who's this?

13:11.659 --> 13:12.659
My girlfriend's bestie.

13:15.859 --> 13:17.460
A bit nosy, huh?

13:18.540 --> 13:19.739
We were cooperating fine,

13:19.739 --> 13:21.019
and you ruined it?

13:21.580 --> 13:22.979
Is that proper business?

13:22.979 --> 13:23.700
What business

13:23.700 --> 13:25.019
needs hand-holding?

13:26.259 --> 13:27.420
Holding hands, what's wrong?

13:28.220 --> 13:29.220
I just touched your hand,

13:29.220 --> 13:29.859
- so what?
- What are you doing?

13:30.220 --> 13:31.019
- I just did it!
- What?

13:31.259 --> 13:31.899
- You…
- I just…

14:08.259 --> 14:10.259
And who are you?

14:11.899 --> 14:13.139
I'm her lawyer.

14:14.580 --> 14:15.100
Sir,

14:15.100 --> 14:16.340
I must remind you.

14:17.100 --> 14:17.979
Under Civil Code,

14:17.979 --> 14:19.060
Art. 1010,

14:19.460 --> 14:20.499
if someone sexually harasses another

14:20.820 --> 14:21.940
against their will

14:22.180 --> 14:23.739
via touch,

14:24.379 --> 14:25.779
the victim can

14:25.779 --> 14:28.180
seek civil damages.

14:30.899 --> 14:32.139
Bringing a lawyer to dinner?

14:32.820 --> 14:33.820
Is she some big shot?

14:35.019 --> 14:36.220
Stop it, let's go.

14:36.220 --> 14:37.060
What about the deal?

14:46.499 --> 14:47.060
You okay?

14:50.139 --> 14:50.580
Come along.

14:54.180 --> 14:54.779
Sorry,

14:55.139 --> 14:56.540
got held up by some

14:56.540 --> 14:57.820
personal stuff earlier.

14:58.619 --> 15:00.300
You're being formal again.

15:00.540 --> 15:01.899
No worries, we were all eating fine.

15:01.899 --> 15:02.700
Right, Huaisong?

15:04.180 --> 15:05.420
Yeah, but you seem late.

15:09.139 --> 15:10.379
Next client meeting.

15:16.619 --> 15:17.300
Right, right.

15:17.899 --> 15:18.300
Well,

15:18.460 --> 15:19.300
thanks for the heads-up.

15:19.300 --> 15:20.220
I'd have forgotten otherwise.

15:20.220 --> 15:21.300
Yu, I've got something to do,

15:21.300 --> 15:22.180
can't send you back.

15:24.420 --> 15:25.060
Let him take you.

15:27.859 --> 15:28.540
No need,

15:28.659 --> 15:29.499
I'll just grab a taxi.

15:29.659 --> 15:30.180
No!

15:30.700 --> 15:31.979
Don't take a taxi, not safe.

15:31.979 --> 15:32.739
What if you

15:32.739 --> 15:34.060
run into those two again? You…

15:39.100 --> 15:39.580
Get in.

15:43.499 --> 15:43.899
Go ahead.

15:45.499 --> 15:46.420
Thanks, Mr. Xu.

16:13.460 --> 16:14.580
Should I tell her?

16:20.139 --> 16:20.739
If you need legal help,

16:20.739 --> 16:21.659
you can

16:22.619 --> 16:23.180
tell me.

16:26.220 --> 16:26.739
Okay.

16:28.499 --> 16:29.379
But for now,

16:29.379 --> 16:30.499
no need.

16:42.460 --> 16:43.180
Mr. Xu,

16:43.739 --> 16:44.460
well,

16:44.739 --> 16:46.139
if you saw your boyfriend

16:46.139 --> 16:47.259
touching another woman's hand,

16:47.820 --> 16:48.859
can you conclude

16:48.859 --> 16:49.619
he's cheating?

16:53.340 --> 16:54.940
Are you sure he's still "boyfriend"?

16:55.379 --> 16:56.300
Of course.

16:58.739 --> 16:59.499
Emotionally, yes,

17:00.420 --> 17:02.540
but legally, evidence isn't enough.

17:03.820 --> 17:04.779
Even hands-on

17:04.779 --> 17:05.420
doesn't prove

17:05.420 --> 17:06.460
he's cheating?

17:07.580 --> 17:09.019
It's not solid proof,

17:09.619 --> 17:10.060
but,

17:11.100 --> 17:12.379
you have the right to break up.

17:15.300 --> 17:16.459
Me, breaking up with him?

17:21.300 --> 17:22.740
Mr. Xu, you misunderstood.

17:22.899 --> 17:23.300
That guy

17:23.300 --> 17:24.580
is my bestie's boyfriend.

17:34.419 --> 17:36.459
Sorry, I misunderstood.

17:37.300 --> 17:39.300
No worries, I was just stressing

17:39.300 --> 17:40.139
whether to send her

17:40.139 --> 17:40.619
the photos.

17:41.100 --> 17:42.379
If I send it and

17:42.699 --> 17:43.699
it's a misunderstanding,

17:43.939 --> 17:44.899
wouldn't that stir trouble?

17:45.699 --> 17:46.780
But if he's really a jerk,

17:46.780 --> 17:47.179
cheating…

17:47.179 --> 17:49.379
If they truly love each other,

17:50.100 --> 17:50.699
one photo

17:50.699 --> 17:52.300
won't break them.

17:53.379 --> 17:54.139
If they already

17:54.139 --> 17:55.340
distrust each other,

17:55.699 --> 17:57.219
even without the photo,

17:57.659 --> 17:58.619
their relationship

17:58.859 --> 18:00.379
would end eventually.

18:02.340 --> 18:03.100
Makes sense.

18:04.619 --> 18:05.219
Mr. Xu,

18:05.540 --> 18:06.419
you really know

18:06.500 --> 18:07.820
love and experience.

18:20.020 --> 18:20.659
Well,

18:21.139 --> 18:22.379
I didn't mean it that way.

18:29.500 --> 18:30.060
I've handled some

18:30.060 --> 18:31.340
divorce cases abroad.

18:32.179 --> 18:32.820
Seen a lot,

18:33.740 --> 18:35.020
got experience.

18:37.740 --> 18:38.340
Oh, yeah.

18:41.820 --> 18:42.980
I might be right, might not.

18:43.740 --> 18:44.740
Think it over

18:45.219 --> 18:46.060
and decide.

18:49.219 --> 18:50.459
Thanks, Mr. Xu.

22:11.699 --> 22:12.899
Sorry, Mr. Xu,

22:13.379 --> 22:14.459
I dozed off.

22:16.139 --> 22:17.300
When did we get here?

22:18.500 --> 22:18.980
Just now,

22:19.659 --> 22:20.300
was about to call you.

22:23.459 --> 22:24.459
Thanks for taking me back.

22:25.740 --> 22:26.260
No problem.

22:44.179 --> 22:45.020
I'll head off now.

22:45.619 --> 22:47.060
Mr. Xu, stay safe.

22:48.379 --> 22:48.859
Bye.

23:14.100 --> 23:14.899
Mingying, what's up?

23:15.980 --> 23:16.659
[Hey, Yu.]

23:16.740 --> 23:17.580
[Got time now?]

23:17.580 --> 23:18.619
[I need to tell you something.]

23:21.020 --> 23:22.899
I happen to have something too.

23:23.540 --> 23:24.859
You go first.

23:25.580 --> 23:27.020
I noticed Cen Sisi

23:27.020 --> 23:28.619
is copying your photos

23:28.619 --> 23:29.659
on social media.

23:30.020 --> 23:30.980
You mean this is

23:30.980 --> 23:32.020
about Cen Sisi?

23:32.500 --> 23:33.340
Yeah, what's up?

23:36.340 --> 23:37.899
Don't you have anything else to say?

23:39.659 --> 23:41.060
You mean Chuan's issue?

23:41.500 --> 23:42.859
He told me as soon as he got home.

23:42.859 --> 23:43.419
He said today

23:43.419 --> 23:44.699
he had dinner with a female boss,

23:44.699 --> 23:45.619
and you saw it.

23:45.899 --> 23:46.899
It's just a misunderstanding.

23:47.619 --> 23:48.139
Nothing serious.

23:48.139 --> 23:49.659
That business deal fell through,

23:49.659 --> 23:50.859
but he can pick up another one.

23:51.740 --> 23:52.939
He just told you

23:53.459 --> 23:54.820
he was having dinner with a female boss?

23:55.219 --> 23:55.780
Yeah.

23:57.139 --> 23:57.699
What's wrong?

23:59.419 --> 24:00.379
Did you see anything else?

24:17.300 --> 24:18.020
Take a look.

24:19.820 --> 24:21.219
He told me this too.

24:21.219 --> 24:22.459
Today they were testing

24:22.459 --> 24:23.540
a hand cream.

24:23.540 --> 24:24.859
He was just testing the product,

24:25.020 --> 24:26.340
but you saw it

24:26.340 --> 24:28.300
and thought he was touching her hand.

24:30.300 --> 24:31.379
So it was the hand cream.

24:33.139 --> 24:34.379
Maybe I did misunderstand.

24:36.219 --> 24:37.060
Don't worry,

24:37.419 --> 24:38.780
if he really cheated,

24:38.780 --> 24:39.540
I'd kick him

24:39.619 --> 24:40.980
out immediately!

24:42.780 --> 24:43.219
Alright.

24:43.419 --> 24:44.780
Keep a close eye, I'll hang up.

24:45.100 --> 24:45.659
[Bye.]

24:47.020 --> 24:48.340
[From now on, let someone else handle]

24:48.340 --> 24:49.340
[offline meetings.]

24:49.699 --> 24:51.219
I'll only do remote testing

24:51.459 --> 24:52.419
and live promotions.

24:52.699 --> 24:54.100
[I'm just using your face]

24:54.100 --> 24:55.939
[to charm female bosses.]

24:56.300 --> 24:57.139
[You're just]

24:57.139 --> 24:58.540
[wasting your advantage.]

24:58.939 --> 25:00.100
[Just playing along,]

25:00.100 --> 25:01.500
[not cheating on your girlfriend.]

25:01.659 --> 25:02.820
[Being so rigid won't make money.]

25:03.139 --> 25:04.540
[Don't whine if your girlfriend]

25:04.540 --> 25:05.100
[thinks you're cheap.]

25:05.100 --> 25:06.500
That's your idea.

25:06.980 --> 25:07.659
My girlfriend and I

25:07.659 --> 25:08.500
are very happy,

25:08.500 --> 25:09.419
no need for your concern.

25:18.260 --> 25:19.260
Done soaking, babe?

25:22.820 --> 25:24.179
The water's cold.

25:24.939 --> 25:26.060
I told you

25:26.060 --> 25:27.419
soaking too long isn't good for health.

25:29.100 --> 25:30.100
Why does it

25:30.100 --> 25:30.980
auto-shut off recently?

25:31.219 --> 25:31.939
I didn't notice.

25:34.780 --> 25:35.740
I bought you a new

25:35.740 --> 25:36.619
saffron foot soak,

25:36.619 --> 25:37.340
coming tomorrow.

25:37.340 --> 25:38.540
Really? Great!

25:38.540 --> 25:39.060
I'm tired of

25:39.060 --> 25:40.060
this mugwort one.

25:41.419 --> 25:42.020
Here.

25:44.060 --> 25:44.980
I'll pour it.

26:23.619 --> 26:24.780
Babe, did you see my phone?

26:24.780 --> 26:25.260
Just now…

26:29.859 --> 26:31.179
Always so forgetful,

26:31.179 --> 26:32.100
can't seem to fix it.

26:32.379 --> 26:33.379
That's why you're here.

26:48.659 --> 26:49.459
Fried chicken's almost here.

26:50.219 --> 26:51.300
Yu's almost here too.

26:51.300 --> 26:52.419
Get ready, okay?

26:53.740 --> 26:54.419
It's only 11,

26:54.419 --> 26:55.340
isn't she supposed to arrive at 12?

26:55.939 --> 26:57.500
She didn't wanna miss

26:57.500 --> 26:58.540
the perfect call time,

26:58.540 --> 26:59.100
so,

26:59.100 --> 27:00.340
she left an hour early.

27:09.500 --> 27:11.060
Why isn't she answering?

27:13.820 --> 27:14.699
- Hello.
- Hello.

27:14.699 --> 27:15.100
Excuse me,

27:15.139 --> 27:16.820
is this Zhikun

27:16.820 --> 27:17.459
Law Firm?

27:17.780 --> 27:18.260
Yes.

27:19.780 --> 27:21.100
This is the…

27:21.300 --> 27:23.219
Xu Huai…

27:23.300 --> 27:24.020
his takeout.

27:26.179 --> 27:26.659
Hi,

27:27.179 --> 27:28.780
is this takeout for Xu Huaisong?

27:29.740 --> 27:30.459
Seems so.

27:30.899 --> 27:31.459
Then give it to me,

27:31.459 --> 27:32.260
I'll bring it up.

27:32.619 --> 27:33.540
Thanks so much.

27:38.020 --> 27:39.020
Answer the phone!

27:47.500 --> 27:48.100
Mr. Xu,

27:48.820 --> 27:49.459
your takeout.

27:50.580 --> 27:51.859
I didn't order any.

27:53.859 --> 27:55.020
It has your name on it.

27:57.619 --> 27:58.659
Then it must be a mistake.

27:58.899 --> 27:59.980
I never order takeout.

28:00.219 --> 28:00.859
Besides, I don't even have

28:00.859 --> 28:01.939
any local food apps.

28:03.980 --> 28:04.859
Here you are.

28:05.459 --> 28:06.300
Yu, you're here.

28:07.580 --> 28:08.540
Where's the fried chicken you ordered?

28:08.859 --> 28:09.619
The cola I bought for you

28:09.619 --> 28:10.500
is already downstairs.

28:10.820 --> 28:11.740
Cola and fried chicken,

28:11.740 --> 28:12.619
a perfect match, bro.

28:12.899 --> 28:13.459
So where's the fried chicken?

28:15.899 --> 28:16.419
Here.

28:17.419 --> 28:18.340
You picked it up?

28:18.580 --> 28:19.740
Great, let's eat together!

28:26.459 --> 28:27.939
[Bro,]

28:27.939 --> 28:29.340
[Yu probably doesn't]

28:29.340 --> 28:30.659
[like you anymore.]

28:31.459 --> 28:32.820
[Even if she does,]

28:33.060 --> 28:34.139
[the person in her heart]

28:34.139 --> 28:36.179
[isn't really you.]

28:37.300 --> 28:38.419
[She probably doesn't even know]

28:38.419 --> 28:39.300
[you like fried chicken.]

28:41.060 --> 28:42.379
[If you showed your true self,]

28:42.859 --> 28:44.419
[could she take it?]

28:46.300 --> 28:48.580
Mr. Liu recently formed a diet group

28:48.580 --> 28:49.659
with colleagues at the firm.

28:50.780 --> 28:51.899
If anyone orders takeout

28:51.899 --> 28:52.859
and gets caught,

28:53.139 --> 28:54.300
they have to chip in a fine

28:54.300 --> 28:54.939
in the company chat.

28:56.419 --> 28:57.500
But no worries, Mr. Liu.

28:57.820 --> 28:59.260
Next time you want to eat,

28:59.740 --> 29:01.300
I can still cover for you

29:02.139 --> 29:03.060
under my name.

29:04.980 --> 29:06.100
Just a reminder,

29:06.820 --> 29:08.699
fried chicken is really unhealthy.

29:09.540 --> 29:10.379
Eat it less from now on.

29:13.619 --> 29:14.139
Got it.

29:14.580 --> 29:16.020
Okay, understood.

29:16.859 --> 29:19.540
Then you stay disciplined, Mr. Xu.

29:19.899 --> 29:20.379
Of course.

29:20.699 --> 29:21.179
Fine.

29:21.500 --> 29:22.179
Here, Yu,

29:22.300 --> 29:23.179
I'll pour you some cola.

29:24.459 --> 29:25.780
Cola and fried chicken.

29:27.139 --> 29:27.659
Perfect!

29:28.740 --> 29:29.260
Thanks.

29:30.619 --> 29:31.139
Mr. Xu,

29:31.619 --> 29:32.619
you shouldn't drink cola either,

29:32.619 --> 29:33.500
it's not healthy.

29:43.100 --> 29:43.859
So good!

29:55.980 --> 29:57.260
Smells amazing!

30:03.899 --> 30:05.659
Mingying, you want a drumstick?

30:05.820 --> 30:06.340
Take it.

30:07.219 --> 30:07.859
Didn't you just say

30:07.859 --> 30:09.260
you were too hungry to eat two?

30:09.459 --> 30:11.219
I want stir-fried eggs with cucumber.

30:11.699 --> 30:12.540
This will do for me.

30:16.939 --> 30:17.820
Give me a drumstick.

30:22.740 --> 30:24.219
[The drumstick I crave,]

30:24.580 --> 30:26.580
[and Huaisong too.]

30:27.100 --> 30:28.340
[I can't have both.]

30:28.619 --> 30:30.980
[So I'll take Huaisong
and forgo the drumstick.]

30:32.659 --> 30:33.379
You really don't want it?

30:34.780 --> 30:35.419
Don't like it.

30:35.780 --> 30:37.060
Then it's mine.

30:48.939 --> 30:49.699
I already ate

30:49.699 --> 30:50.459
before going out,

30:50.659 --> 30:51.459
so I'm not hungry.

30:52.020 --> 30:53.340
Mr. Liu, eat more.

30:54.780 --> 30:55.419
You're not eating either?

30:56.100 --> 30:56.699
Then, Yu,

30:57.899 --> 30:59.139
drink this beverage.

31:01.179 --> 31:02.100
So good!

31:03.179 --> 31:03.740
Mr. Xu,

31:04.500 --> 31:05.379
drink some.

31:05.859 --> 31:07.020
This should be your go-to,

31:07.020 --> 31:07.740
and it's a healthier pick too.

31:08.340 --> 31:08.859
Thanks.

31:11.459 --> 31:14.379
Serving you a pure black coffee,

31:14.899 --> 31:17.780
wishing you an energetic day.

31:32.859 --> 31:34.020
Last time, Mr. Xu,

31:34.020 --> 31:35.580
you drank coffee like it was cola.

31:36.459 --> 31:37.219
Isn't it bitter?

31:38.619 --> 31:39.179
I'm used to it.

31:48.820 --> 31:50.340
What are you drinking, Mr. Xu?

31:51.820 --> 31:52.659
Black coffee?

31:53.419 --> 31:54.340
I've never seen anyone

31:54.340 --> 31:55.740
drink it in such

31:55.740 --> 31:56.580
big sips.

31:59.340 --> 31:59.939
I'm used to it.

32:06.100 --> 32:07.419
Some things,

32:08.300 --> 32:09.340
only you know

32:10.699 --> 32:12.219
if they're bitter.

32:14.659 --> 32:16.540
Right, Mr. Xu?

32:22.139 --> 32:22.780
So good.

32:28.820 --> 32:29.459
I'll call now.

32:45.379 --> 32:46.500
Hello, I'm Ruan Yu.

32:46.780 --> 32:48.020
Are you Cen Sisi?

32:48.859 --> 32:49.899
[Yes, Yu.]

32:50.300 --> 32:51.379
[I've saved your number.]

32:52.179 --> 32:52.939
Identity confirmed.

32:55.939 --> 32:57.139
You got a sec to talk?

32:58.219 --> 32:59.139
[Yeah, go ahead.]

33:00.820 --> 33:01.459
Here's the thing.

33:02.060 --> 33:03.260
I was gonna have my lawyer

33:03.619 --> 33:05.139
handle the settlement,

33:05.659 --> 33:06.419
but I figured

33:06.980 --> 33:07.540
I should

33:07.540 --> 33:08.419
talk to you first.

33:09.659 --> 33:10.780
A film company

33:10.899 --> 33:12.060
approached me recently

33:12.060 --> 33:13.500
about adapting my book.

33:25.100 --> 33:25.780
Well,

33:26.179 --> 33:27.260
they want this scandal

33:27.260 --> 33:28.859
cleaned up,

33:29.179 --> 33:29.939
otherwise,

33:30.179 --> 33:31.580
the adaptation's off.

33:32.459 --> 33:33.139
[Yu,]

33:33.340 --> 33:34.659
[signal's bad here,]

33:35.100 --> 33:36.459
[let's talk face-to-face.]

33:37.020 --> 33:39.020
[How about 1 PM]

33:39.020 --> 33:39.500
[at Nanhu Café?]

33:39.859 --> 33:40.899
[It's close to your place.]

33:42.459 --> 33:43.859
Sure, see you there.

33:47.859 --> 33:49.179
She might be on guard.

33:49.980 --> 33:51.219
It takes about

33:51.219 --> 33:51.859
20 mins

33:51.859 --> 33:52.780
to get there.

33:53.179 --> 33:54.139
I'll head over,

33:54.139 --> 33:54.859
don't want any slip-ups.

33:55.419 --> 33:56.219
You going solo?

33:58.899 --> 33:59.899
Should be fine.

34:04.060 --> 34:05.020
You only get one shot.

34:06.580 --> 34:07.179
I'll go with you.

34:17.540 --> 34:18.100
Recorder.

34:18.940 --> 34:19.779
Push up to record,

34:20.139 --> 34:20.860
down to save.

34:41.179 --> 34:42.060
Thanks, Mr. Xu.

35:13.819 --> 35:15.339
I thought coaxing info over the phone

35:15.819 --> 35:16.699
would be easy.

35:17.580 --> 35:18.699
But now,

35:20.460 --> 35:21.659
my heart's racing.

35:28.259 --> 35:29.420
Let's do some eye exercises.

35:34.500 --> 35:35.860
Looks like it works

35:36.540 --> 35:37.299
in your novel.

36:07.699 --> 36:09.380
[Sorry, I grabbed the wrong one.]

36:10.540 --> 36:12.020
The wrong one.

36:13.659 --> 36:14.179
Then,

36:15.179 --> 36:16.739
who's the right one?

36:22.619 --> 36:23.259
Jerk!

36:29.100 --> 36:29.940
Novels are

36:31.060 --> 36:31.900
all smoke and mirrors.

36:36.420 --> 36:38.060
[Eye exercises are bogus…]

36:39.460 --> 36:41.940
[and so is 'liking me?']

36:46.619 --> 36:48.299
[Eye exercises don't work at all.]

36:49.619 --> 36:50.900
[That day, yelling 'jerk']

36:50.900 --> 36:51.900
[a hundred times]

36:52.580 --> 36:54.500
[finally calmed me down.]

37:15.699 --> 37:16.259
Yu,

37:17.339 --> 37:18.779
thanks for giving me this chance

37:19.020 --> 37:20.259
to explain in person.

37:22.980 --> 37:25.139
I've thought it through, Sisi.

37:26.339 --> 37:27.460
Settlement's fine.

37:29.699 --> 37:31.060
But my lawyer isn't just

37:31.380 --> 37:32.659
looking out for me,

37:32.980 --> 37:34.139
they're thinking about the adaptation.

37:35.259 --> 37:36.259
To protect

37:36.339 --> 37:37.779
the adaptation,

37:38.699 --> 37:39.420
they want you

37:39.420 --> 37:40.699
to admit in your apology

37:41.739 --> 37:43.219
that you not only posted

37:43.219 --> 37:44.219
slanderous long posts about me

37:44.699 --> 37:46.179
but also stirred online attacks.

37:47.339 --> 37:47.739
I…

37:48.739 --> 37:49.900
I didn't.

37:53.420 --> 37:54.940
I know this statement

37:54.940 --> 37:56.060
is rough,

37:57.540 --> 37:58.779
but the production company

37:58.779 --> 37:59.699
says if we

37:59.699 --> 38:01.339
can't settle, they'll sue.

38:02.500 --> 38:04.500
But Yu, I…

38:06.179 --> 38:08.420
I didn't aim to attack you.

38:09.580 --> 38:10.540
When I posted that,

38:10.540 --> 38:11.460
I honestly

38:11.900 --> 38:12.940
thought that's

38:12.940 --> 38:13.779
how it was.

38:15.020 --> 38:15.900
I had no idea

38:15.900 --> 38:16.980
you are Lily Vale.

38:17.619 --> 38:18.540
That post

38:18.540 --> 38:19.380
then went viral

38:19.380 --> 38:20.299
on its own,

38:20.659 --> 38:21.900
had nothing to do with me.

38:22.299 --> 38:23.940
Just the internet running wild.

38:27.179 --> 38:27.739
Sisi,

38:28.860 --> 38:30.020
the web isn't lawless.

38:30.659 --> 38:31.460
Everything leaves

38:31.460 --> 38:32.619
a trail.

38:33.299 --> 38:34.540
Even if you deny it now,

38:34.980 --> 38:36.020
it'll show up

38:36.179 --> 38:37.060
in the investigation later.

38:39.739 --> 38:40.460
We went to

38:40.580 --> 38:41.819
the same school.

38:42.779 --> 38:43.739
You're my junior.

38:45.420 --> 38:46.739
Of course I don't want things

38:47.659 --> 38:48.619
to get messy.

38:50.699 --> 38:51.179
So…

38:53.259 --> 38:54.299
Yu,

38:55.659 --> 38:57.179
could you drop the case for now?

38:58.540 --> 39:00.179
You can still

39:00.299 --> 39:01.380
have your lawyer

39:01.380 --> 39:02.580
check things out later.

39:03.179 --> 39:04.299
Let's settle this quietly,

39:04.299 --> 39:05.179
no drama.

39:05.580 --> 39:06.619
Isn't that better?

39:10.179 --> 39:11.420
That could work.

39:13.299 --> 39:14.420
But if I drop it,

39:15.139 --> 39:16.460
someone sneaky

39:16.860 --> 39:18.460
might twist it against me

39:19.259 --> 39:20.139
and stir up The Poet

39:20.139 --> 39:21.139
to sue.

39:21.699 --> 39:22.580
What then?

39:24.980 --> 39:26.980
You're overthinking it, isn't it?

39:40.339 --> 39:41.659
[If things stall,]

39:41.900 --> 39:43.500
[try to switch gears]

39:43.980 --> 39:45.020
[and change the topic.]

39:45.020 --> 39:46.179
[Play along with her,]

39:46.380 --> 39:47.540
[let her guard down.]

39:59.259 --> 39:59.819
Sisi.

40:04.819 --> 40:05.500
Actually,

40:07.339 --> 40:08.619
I've been having a really rough time.

40:12.179 --> 40:12.779
I know,

40:14.219 --> 40:15.500
at this rate,

40:17.819 --> 40:18.739
the adaptation rights

40:18.739 --> 40:19.699
won't sell.

40:20.299 --> 40:21.139
If this keeps up,

40:22.139 --> 40:22.980
the site could

40:22.980 --> 40:24.259
drop me any minute.

40:27.380 --> 40:28.739
That won't happen.

40:30.139 --> 40:31.699
You're the cash cow.

40:33.580 --> 40:34.900
Authors come and go,

40:34.900 --> 40:35.659
fast.

40:36.380 --> 40:37.819
Once Qianhe kicks me out,

40:39.139 --> 40:40.219
no other site will

40:40.219 --> 40:41.100
touch me either.

40:45.699 --> 40:47.500
Yu, you worry too much.

40:47.900 --> 40:49.299
Even if the worst happens,

40:49.460 --> 40:50.179
Shican

40:50.179 --> 40:51.699
wouldn't just sit back.

40:52.860 --> 40:54.380
After all, he owes you

40:54.380 --> 40:55.299
from back in school.

40:56.060 --> 40:56.580
Right?

40:57.580 --> 40:58.659
He's so busy right now,

40:59.699 --> 41:01.219
he won't bother with stuff like this.

41:04.860 --> 41:05.819
I was thinking,

41:08.420 --> 41:10.179
if you really hired the army of fans,

41:11.100 --> 41:12.619
at least with Shican in the loop,

41:13.699 --> 41:15.100
I could still appeal to you.

41:22.980 --> 41:23.619
Or…

41:26.739 --> 41:27.980
you could just beg me, right?

41:34.139 --> 41:35.060
So it was you.

41:38.699 --> 41:39.779
You knew from the start

41:39.779 --> 41:40.580
that I was Lily Vale.

41:42.819 --> 41:43.779
I said I didn't know,

41:44.259 --> 41:45.259
and you didn't believe me, right?

41:48.580 --> 41:51.179
Didn't you say back in college

41:51.580 --> 41:52.339
you saw my article

41:52.339 --> 41:53.420
in a magazine

41:53.420 --> 41:54.500
and that inspired your dream?

41:56.500 --> 41:57.420
You're making yourself

41:57.420 --> 41:58.659
sound too heroic.

42:00.420 --> 42:01.980
You were copying back then, right?

42:09.219 --> 42:10.460
How can a copied story

42:11.020 --> 42:12.299
get so popular?

42:13.900 --> 42:14.819
I just wanted

42:14.819 --> 42:15.739
the truth out.

42:17.219 --> 42:18.179
Didn't expect

42:18.779 --> 42:20.500
you'd crumble so easily.

42:25.540 --> 42:26.179
I only hired

42:26.179 --> 42:27.819
a few bots,

42:29.100 --> 42:29.779
and you just…

42:33.580 --> 42:34.259
broke down?

42:41.259 --> 42:41.779
Come down!

42:41.860 --> 42:42.860
Chase me!

42:45.860 --> 42:47.339
Sorry, sis.

43:23.540 --> 43:24.500
Fun with the phone?

43:25.179 --> 43:27.380
Not bad. Haven't you tried it?

43:29.860 --> 43:30.699
Lend it to me for a sec.

43:39.619 --> 43:40.420
Caught red-handed.

43:41.619 --> 43:43.900
No excuses, hand it over.

43:53.460 --> 43:54.460
Director…

43:55.259 --> 43:55.860
Xu Huaishi!

43:57.580 --> 43:58.420
You're too much!

44:00.299 --> 44:01.739
You… you're really something!

44:01.739 --> 44:02.940
You actually handed
my phone to the teacher?

44:05.460 --> 44:07.739
So this phone's yours?

44:08.060 --> 44:08.779
Name's the same,

44:08.860 --> 44:09.500
no switching,

44:10.139 --> 44:10.900
yours truly.

44:12.659 --> 44:13.460
Never thought

44:14.619 --> 44:15.139
you'd be into

44:15.139 --> 44:16.259
male celebs batting their lashes.

44:18.500 --> 44:19.139
No laughing!

44:26.540 --> 44:27.619
That's my freedom.

44:30.420 --> 44:31.219
Freedom, huh?

44:32.179 --> 44:32.860
There's words here too.

44:35.259 --> 44:36.540
'Shican,'

44:36.619 --> 44:37.460
'I love you forever.'

44:37.860 --> 44:38.819
Is this your freedom too?

44:43.100 --> 44:43.779
This…

44:45.219 --> 44:46.259
I wrote it too.

44:46.980 --> 44:47.460
Well.

44:48.219 --> 44:49.060
So you wrote it.

44:49.860 --> 44:51.100
Then I wonder,

44:52.020 --> 44:53.460
why's your phone wallpaper

44:53.860 --> 44:54.339
her with

44:54.339 --> 44:55.619
a male star?

44:59.380 --> 45:00.100
What's that about?

45:01.380 --> 45:01.819
I…

45:03.940 --> 45:05.219
I'm shipping them.

45:05.380 --> 45:06.779
You can respond to anything, right?

45:07.179 --> 45:07.819
No laughing!

45:09.020 --> 45:10.339
You two, come to my office.

45:10.779 --> 45:11.659
No going home after school.

45:11.860 --> 45:12.460
Call your parents!

45:13.060 --> 45:14.779
[Log into your Huawei account first.]

45:15.060 --> 45:15.860
What the hell account!

45:24.659 --> 45:25.259
Thanks.

45:26.219 --> 45:27.020
For what?

45:27.819 --> 45:28.619
Didn't help you anyway.

45:29.619 --> 45:30.619
I'm not talking about that.

45:31.259 --> 45:31.900
Then what?

45:35.139 --> 45:36.179
You actually said

45:36.460 --> 45:37.940
Shican and I are a ship.
